OL,6,FFour faults were detected in a safety
OL,7,Fsystem for a train involved in a fatal
OL,8,Fcrash in mid-Wales, investigators said.
OL,10,FHoses fitted to the Transport for
OL,11,FWales (TfW) train to discharge sand
OL,12,Fwhen wheels slide during braking were
OL,13,F"blocked", the Rail Accident
OL,14,FInvestigation Branch (RAIB) said in an
OL,15,Finterim report.
OL,17,FThe investigators said: "This fault
OL,18,Fwould have prevented sand from being
OL,19,Fejected from the hoses."
