OL,6,FTwo plates which measure the flow rate
OL,7,Fof sand were incorrectly installed,
OL,8,Fwith both upside down and one
OL,9,Fmisaligned.
OL,11,FTwo electrical faults were also
OL,12,Fdiscovered.
OL,14,FThe train with the failed safety
OL,15,Fsystem was travelling at about 24mph
OL,16,Fwhen it collided head-on with another
OL,17,FTfW train travelling at around 6mph
OL,18,Fnear Talerddig in Powys on October 21
OL,19,Flast year.
