OL,6,FPassenger David Tudor Evans, 66, died
OL,7,Fand four other people were seriously
OL,8,Fhurt.
OL,10,FThose seriously injured included the
OL,11,Fguard of the train with the faulty
OL,12,Fsafety system ` who was standing up at
OL,13,Fthe time of the crash ` and the driver
OL,14,Fof the other train, who was trying to
OL,15,Fleave the driving cab when the crash
OL,16,Fhappened, and became trapped.
OL,18,FA further 23 people received minor
OL,19,Finjuries.
