OL,6,FThe driver then made an emergency
OL,7,Fbrake demand, which remained in place
OL,8,Funtil the crash.
OL,10,FThe train passed through the loop and
OL,11,Frejoined the single line, sliding for
OL,12,Faround 900 metres downhill before the
OL,13,Fcollision occurred.
OL,15,FInvestigators found the sanding hoses
OL,16,Fwere blocked with leaves and debris
OL,17,Ffrom trees.
