OL,6,FA "basic check" of the system was
OL,7,Fcarried out the day before the crash,
OL,8,Fwhich "suggests that the sand hoses
OL,9,Fwere not blocked at this time", the
OL,10,Freport stated.
OL,12,FIt also found the driver of the
OL,13,Fwestbound train was not able to check
OL,14,Fthe safety systems underneath as it
OL,15,Fwas parked adjacent to a station.
OL,17,FFollowing the crash, Network Rail said
OL,18,Fone of its railhead treatment trains `
OL,19,Fwhich tackle autumn leaf fall ` ran
OL,20,Falong the line and passing loop the
OL,21,Fnight before the crash.
