OL,6,FThe RAIB said its investigation will
OL,7,Fconsider several aspects, such as the
OL,8,Fsanding systems and the cause and
OL,9,Fseverity of low adhesion at Talerddig.
OL,11,FTransport for Wales and Network Rail
OL,12,Fsay they are fulling cooperating with
OL,13,Fthe investigation. In a joint
OL,14,Fstatement they said:
